# SIXMEN Database

## Memory Scope

This rule must keep active:

- **Scope governed:** ERD canonical, migration safety, SKU naming, FK/index/CHECK, import/export shape.
- **Canonical context:** `docs/erp/phases/GD0_Nen_tang/ERD.md` · `docs/erp/phases/GD1_Kho_SX/ERD.md` · `docs/ai-agent/reference/doc-map.md` · `sixmen-governance.mdc`.
- **Required project memory:** `product_variants.sku` canonical · `variant.code` deprecated · inventory/NPL balance chỉ qua critical services · PostgreSQL 16 · migration-note trước Backend DDL.
- **Deprecated / rejected:** `docs/erp/core/03_SRS.md` §3 DDL làm chuẩn schema · drop column prod không backup · hard delete movement/audit.
- **Applies to:** `database/**`, `**/ERD.md`, `**/migration-note.md`.
- **Does not apply to:** pure UI không đụng schema; business rule only → BA/Architect.
- **Conflict handling:** defer governance + data-safety; ERD conflict → stop, không chọn ngầm.
- **Stop condition:** schema source không rõ · drop/purge core data · migration prod không backup/approval.

## Purpose

Design/review ERD, schema, constraints, indexes, migration notes, import/export data shape.

